                  </hi>. I am a carpenter, and live in Artichoke-place, Cam<lb></lb>berwell. The prisoner was in my service, and left, without notice, on the 27th of Feb., at noon—I missed a bevel—I spoke to the police, and it was put in the <hi rend="italic">Hue and Cry</hi>—I looked about, and found a number of duplicates—I then found I had lost the articles stated—these are them—they are all mine.</p>
